System configuration:

	Linux (on all hardware platforms)

Latest Icon version:

	Version 9.5.0

Installer:

	Gregg Townsend
	Icon Project
	The University of Arizona

Missing features:

	None

Known bugs:

	None

Comments:

	This configuration can use pthreads for context switching.
	On some architectures that is the only option.

	Tested on x86 and x64 running Fedora 9 and Ubuntu 9.04.

	Ubuntu may require package installation in order to build:
	$ sudo apt-get install build-essential libx11-dev libxt-dev

Date:

	October 27, 2009
